icity generated within the metered boundaries of each balancing authority.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idc067c581-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s18772/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Real-time data dissemination","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"To the maximum extent practicable, the system established under paragraph (1) shall disseminate data—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idc067c582-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s18772/b/3/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" on a real-time basis; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idc067c583-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s18772/b/3/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" through an application programming interface that is publicly accessible.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idc067c584-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s18772/b/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Complementary efforts","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The system established under paragraph (1) shall complement any existing data dissemination efforts of the Administrator that make use of electricity generation data, such as electricity demand by subregion and electricity interchange with directly interconnected balancing authorities.","childr